| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5008 — Recovery Inhibition (VanHelsing)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3301dd74-2a84-5787-93ba-ecf2412b0180"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
